OL,3,CSark could run out of fresh water if
OL,4,Cpopulation rises
OL,6,FSark could run out of water if future
OL,7,Fhousing developments go ahead, a
OL,8,Freport from a UK expert has warned.
OL,10,FThe independent study found that a
OL,11,Fproposed growth in the population, to
OL,12,F700 people, would put great pressure
OL,13,Fon the island's boreholes and wells.
OL,15,FIts author, Dr Derek Clarke from
OL,16,FSouthampton University, adds: "If the
OL,17,Fpopulation rose to 700 people, the
OL,18,Fincreased demands for water combined
OL,19,Fwith the impacts of Climate Change may
OL,20,Fplace impossible demands on the
OL,21,Favailable groundwater."
