OL,6,FJo Birch from La Societe Serquiaise
OL,7,Fsays residents will have to work hard
OL,8,Fto make the supply sustainable in the
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FShe explains: "We can't obviously
OL,12,Fbuild a reservoir, but I think we
OL,13,Fcould make the residents aware to save
OL,14,Fwater.
