OL,6,F"I've lived in dry places where any
OL,7,Fbuilding has to have some underground
OL,8,Fwater storage clipped from the roof,
OL,9,Fso I think most it's probably a
OL,10,Fquestion of making people aware that
OL,11,Fwe could run out of water. That would
OL,12,Fbe pretty desperate."
OL,14,FThe report was commissioned by
OL,15,Fislander Jane Norwich in the spring of
OL,16,F2024 and information was gathered over
OL,17,Fa three-day visit to Sark.
