OL,3,CSark could run out of fresh water if
OL,4,Cpopulation rises
OL,6,FHe says: "We know friends of ours who
OL,7,Fare prone to running out of water,
OL,8,Fparticularly during the dry years and
OL,9,Fhave to bring in water with a bowser,
OL,10,Fwhich is a frightening thought.
OL,12,F"So we have a huge amount of respect
OL,13,Ffor the use of water."
OL,15,FHowever, the study does provide a
OL,16,Fnumber of recommendations as well.
OL,18,FIt suggests that an assessment should
OL,19,Fbe made to identify the most
OL,20,Fproductive boreholes around Sark.
