OL,3,CSark could run out of fresh water if
OL,4,Cpopulation rises
OL,6,FIt is currently not possible to
OL,7,Fdetermine how the groundwater recovers
OL,8,Fafter a drought summer so the report
OL,9,Frecommends the island reinstate a
OL,10,Fgroundwater monitoring system to gain
OL,11,Fmore information.
OL,13,FAny new builds and major housing
OL,14,Frenovations should also require water
OL,15,Fsaving technologies to reduce
OL,16,Fconsumption and the island should
OL,17,Fintroduce a water development fee.
